title: Flight Simulator 2020 - Addon Spotlight - Max Verstappen Livery
description:
In this how to we are going to look at the Max Verstappen livery for the CJ4. The livery is based on the aircraft of F1 driver Max Verstappen and is looking pretty nice.

If you want to be the pilot from Max Verstappen yourself download the livery from the site below: 
https://flightsim.to/file/18753/max-verstappen-s-falcon-900ex-cj4-version
